data.description: In a quiet cul-de-sac sits this beautiful two story home, ready and waiting for your family to make it your own. Polished travertine style tile graces the entire first floor. Off the entry is the office/study with a bay window area providing a nice view of your community. The spacious kitchen boasts oak cabinets with ample storage & topped with black granite countertops. There is also a breakfast bar for quick service on busy mornings. The kitchen is open to the living area so you don't miss out on any excitement and or warm family moments in front of your gas log fireplace. There is an extra room off of the kitchen which can be used as a dining room for a quiet, more private experience. This extra room can also be used as a bedroom, gym or playroom keeping the kiddies secure & close to the homes central base of operation. Spacious upper bedrooms each have their own private bath and walk in closet. The only carpet in the home is on the stairs for traction and noise dampening.
